WEBVTT

00:02.500 --> 00:04.980
[aircraft approaching]

00:05.060 --> 00:06.420
[explosion]

00:08.420 --> 00:10.900
[people shouting in Arabic]

00:10.980 --> 00:12.580
[siren wailing]

00:19.820 --> 00:21.780
[shouting continues]

00:29.260 --> 00:31.620
[indistinct chatter]

00:36.580 --> 00:37.700
[man in English] Take and go.

00:40.620 --> 00:41.980
Take him, take him, take him, take him.

00:42.740 --> 00:44.460
[men chanting in Arabic]

00:47.660 --> 00:49.500
[explosion]

00:49.580 --> 00:52.380
[man yelling in Arabic]

00:54.000 --> 01:00.074
